* In {{ill|Buddhism|ja|仏教|qq=draft}}, the deity is {{ill|Seimen Kongō|ja|青面金剛|qq=draft}}.

== History (Yūshi) ==
With {{ill|Sarutahiko Ōkami|ja|猿田彦大神|qq=draft}} as the principal deity, the shrine was transferred to its present location from the Koushin Shrine in {{ill|Karatsu|ja|唐津市|qq=draft}} in February of Genbun 2 (1737).

